oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Deeker Brothers Store
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of a mule-drawn wagon parked in front of the Deeker Brothers Store in Petros. Two unidentified men can be seen sitting on top of several sacks being hauled in the wagon.
